{
  "stem": "617.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, some of us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'm not saying that the whole camp did.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But some of us were fasting and working and came back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it wasn't nighttime yet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was like-- so we were-- we went to get our ration and our soup.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were sitting in the-- outside the tent and waiting until we could see stars so we could eat.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we did.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we used to see planes flying overhead, you know, when we were working.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we would always wonder, are these the American planes?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Are they Russian?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Are they German?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, we were always hoping that soon, soon, soon, we'll be freed, and this is what we were talking about all the time.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'd like to go back to Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Do you remember what else you did besides fast?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Did anybody pray?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No prayer books and no praying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just what we knew by heart.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the lady who we befriended who was managing the kitchen, like, when we friended-- like, she befriended us in-- in Stutthof.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When she came over, like, we were sitting-- like I said, we weren't existing, as far as the camp was concerned, like, because they thought that they-- they finished with us.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we went into this bunk, and like to this place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was also in that place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And before she came over to us, she heard us pray, my sister and I.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, every Saturday night before it's out, before Shabbos is out, we always say [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like, because I remember with my mother, [CRIES] every Saturday night, we used to sit.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was in shul, in the synagogue, and she would sit with us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all together, we would say [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
